Event Request
Come Enjoy One of Our Many Events!
Events
A perfect outing is par for the course.
Located in the heart of Miami and designed by Mark Mahannah, the Miccosukee Golf & Country Club offers 27 challenging holes of golf, surrounded by Florida‚Äôs unique lush beauty. It‚Äôs unquestionably the best value around and the perfect venue for your next group or business outing.
Anyone can play.
Everyone is welcome. Our course is open to club members and the public. Since the beginning, we‚Äôve coordinated events that range from corporate to charitable with groups and are quite pleased to see them returning year after year.
Choose the time. Choose the place.
To secure your preferred date and course, simply provide us with advanced notice. We suggest that you plan your outing during the spring, summer or fall months as the winter months are most popular and tend to fill up quickly. However, with 27 holes to choose from, it‚Äôs possible to create the outing of your dreams, weekday or weekend!
Your players do not have to play like a top PGA/LPGA pro.
Although we have had hundreds of the finest PGA and LPGA golfers challenged by our course, we understand that not everyone enjoys the game at the same level. Simply inform us of the caliber of players you intend to have and we‚Äôll suggest the proper 18 holes, which are guaranteed to give everyone a super outing.
The size of your group does not matter to us; your satisfaction matters.
We welcome groups that are both large and small.
